15
00:01:37,972 --> 00:01:40,225
So why can't he do it?

16
00:01:40,308 --> 00:01:41,893
JIN HYEONG-U

17
00:01:41,976 --> 00:01:44,103
APPLICANT'S TESTIFIER: YANG JONG-HOON

18
00:01:44,187 --> 00:01:45,980
