the presumption of innocence.

44
00:03:29,083 --> 00:03:31,586
It's not to break
the presumption of innocence.

45
00:03:31,669 --> 00:03:34,839
The people commissioned us
as investigative authorities,

46
00:03:34,923 --> 00:03:37,383
